A program in C++ to input a string and print it.
Enter the string : Welcome to String
The string is : Welcome to String

************************************************************************

#include<iostream>
#include<string.h>
int main()
{
	char a[100];
	std::cout<<"Enter the string : ";
	//Taking user input
	gets(a);
	std::cout<<"The string is : "<<a;
	return 0;
}

Output is :
Enter the string : Hacktoberfest is fun.
The string is : Hacktoberfest is fun.
